{"tid":42119,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"東京食肆為員工 平安夜禁情侶光顧","createTime":"2016-12-16T12:08:50.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-16T13:49:05.000Z","uid":36494,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"10bad6422b7d19249c248e51d9f600050aad8bfb","tid":42119,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T12:08:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20161216&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=56054305\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20161216%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D56054305&d=H5S4o0Ff8XTpADkL962R5oscwJTI%2BQouKF8MUrnyvY0%3D&h=2d061f81\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20161216%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D56054305&h=69479da0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20161216&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=56054305</a><br />\n<br />\n【毒男福音】平安夜禁情侶光顧 東京食肆咁做係為員工！<br />\n<br />\n聖誕節是做生意的旺季，但日本東京八王子市一間意粉店就反傳統，講明平安夜拒絕情侶光顧，並貼出圖文並茂的告示，叫人哭笑不得。<br />\n<br />\n「Spaghetti PiaPia」位於「京王八王子站」附近，店方最先在2014年貼出謝絕情侶的告示，成為一時熱話，今年亦繼續這份「反傳統」。雖然距離平安夜仍有一段日子，店方已在本周三貼出告示，寫道：「今年也是甚麼也沒有。由於本店職員感到悔恨，故容許我們平安夜拒絕情侶入店。」告示上畫有一男一女沐浴愛河的公仔，上面更附有紅色大交叉，怨憤之情不言而喻。<br />\n<br />\n店方沒有進一步闡明為何店員會感到悔恨，不過網民大呼這個做法「有趣」之餘，也猜想是因為店員都是單身人士，為免佳節陪感落寞，所以店方才有這個做法。<br />\n<br />\n今年已是店方連續3年張貼這種告示，店方指，告示只是張貼了一日就經已收到客人反應。平安夜光顧的顧客將會獲得「賢者轉世卡」一張，卡的內容店方大賣關子，說要等到客人當日光顧才公佈。"},{"pid":"b1c167fa80f696a67f2e687e592186b7a13bd6cc","tid":42119,"uid":6644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T12:18:32.000Z","msg":"Ho ball<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b867c4394d65887e1cd889c7378707e5fc97a89","tid":42119,"uid":35919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T12:21:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"760af2344f2393f793ef9f1138b6b3b383ec3d20","tid":42119,"uid":41353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T12:23:19.000Z","msg":"香港都需要<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cbd23519fc17b0ec2a4b3dfb73d2bd8ebb17311","tid":42119,"uid":14341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T12:24:27.000Z","msg":"吸引單身食客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fce7c38cd08194da66568ca87e1ac2e0f417e60","tid":42119,"uid":56729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T12:25:57.000Z","msg":"憤怒的葡萄 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n留名睇下晴報會點寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bcc1eb30d7b617029cd91ac30ed4753659268a0","tid":42119,"uid":58670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T12:27:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3826582ce3edc680a270969a4023c017f518bf47","tid":42119,"uid":21917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T13:49:05.000Z","msg":"香港係唔會有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}